  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-text">WHO WE ARE</span>
        <div class="gold-divider-small"></div>
      </div>
      <h1>Meet the Crew Behind SeaForth</h1>
      <p class="hero-description">
        We're Abby and Savanna—a creative strategist and a data analyst who joined forces to build something different. A marketing agency that doesn't just talk strategy—we live it, breathe it, and deliver it.
      </p>
      <p class="hero-description">
        Based in San Diego, we help businesses grow smarter with marketing that's equal parts creative and analytical. No fluff. No guesswork. Just results.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="team-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-text">THE TEAM</span>
        <div class="gold-divider-small"></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="team-headline">The Dynamic Duo</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Where Creative Vision Meets Analytical Precision</p>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <article class="team-card">
          <div class="team-image-wrapper">
            <img 
              src="/images/Abby.png" 
              alt="Abby Lehr, Co-Founder and Chief Creative Officer" 
              width="560" 
              height="560" 
              class="team-image" 
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="team-content">
            <h3>Abby Lehr</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Co-Founder & Chief Creative Officer (CCO)</p>
            <p class="team-bio">
              I'm the creative force behind SeaForth—the one who turns big ideas into bold campaigns. At 22, I've built a career bringing brands to life online with websites that wow, social content that stops the scroll, and ad campaigns that actually convert.
            </p>
            <p class="team-bio">
              I believe great marketing should feel effortless, look stunning, and drive real results. That's what I build for every client—digital experiences that don't just exist, they perform.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="team-card">
          <div class="team-image-wrapper">
            <img 
              src="/images/Savanna.png" 
              alt="Savanna Spayd, Co-Founder and Chief Analytics Officer" 
              width="560" 
              height="560" 
              class="team-image" 
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="team-content">
            <h3>Savanna Spayd</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Co-Founder & Chief Analytics Officer (CAO)</p>
            <p class="team-bio">
              I'm the analytical backbone of SeaForth—the one who makes sure every campaign is backed by data, optimized for performance, and built to scale. I turn complex metrics into clear insights that drive smarter decisions and measurable growth.
            </p>
            <p class="team-bio">
              Numbers don't lie, and I make sure they tell the story of what's working, what's not, and where your next big opportunity is hiding.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-text">OUR STORY</span>
        <div class="gold-divider-small"></div>
      </div>
      <h2>How We Got Here</h2>
      <div class="story-content">
        <p class="story-text">
          SeaForth Strategies was born from a simple realization: most marketing agencies talk a big game 
          but fail to deliver results. We saw too many businesses pouring money into campaigns that looked 
          pretty but didn't perform.
        </p>
        <p class="story-text">
          So we decided to do things differently. We combined Abby's creative vision with Savanna's 
          analytical precision to create a marketing agency that doesn't just make noise—it makes an impact. 
          Every strategy we build is rooted in data, every creative decision is intentional, and every 
          campaign is designed to drive real, measurable growth.
        </p>
        <p class="story-text">
          Based in sunny San Diego, we work with ambitious businesses who are ready to level up. Whether 
          you're a startup looking to make your mark or an established brand ready to scale, we bring the 
          perfect blend of creativity and analytics to chart your course to success.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Section -->
  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-text">BY THE NUMBERS</span>
        <div class="gold-divider-small"></div>
      </div>
      <h2>Results That Speak Volumes</h2>
      <p class="stats-intro">Our success is measured by the success of our clients. Here's what we've achieved together.</p>
      
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="150">0</div>
          <div class="stat-suffix">%</div>
          <p class="stat-label">Average ROI Increase</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="50">0</div>
          <div class="stat-suffix">+</div>
          <p class="stat-label">Happy Clients</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="2.5">0</div>
          <div class="stat-suffix">M+</div>
          <p class="stat-label">In Revenue Generated</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="98">0</div>
          <div class="stat-suffix">%</div>
          <p class="stat-label">Client Satisfaction Rate</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Values Section -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-text">OUR VALUES</span>
        <div class="gold-divider-small"></div>
      </div>
      <h2>What Drives Us</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Results Over Everything</h3>
          <p>We don't do marketing for the sake of marketing. Every campaign is built to deliver measurable results and real ROI.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Driven Decisions</h3>
          <p>Gut feelings don't scale. We let the numbers guide our strategy and optimize relentlessly based on performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Partnership, Not Transactions</h3>
          <p>We're not here for one-off projects. We build long-term partnerships and invest in your success like it's our own.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
          </div>
